          java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,​java.util.ArrayList<IEmployee>> rentalWaitingList
          Hash map indexed by the vehicle id and containing for each vehicle, the list of employees renting or waiting for the rental. If the array list is empty, then the car is not rented. The first element of the array list is the current renter. The next elements are the employees waiting for renting this car.
